[
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p000.jpg",
    "text": "WORDINARY Episode 7"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p001.jpg",
    "text": "About a year ago,\nI transferred into Wellston Private High School"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p002.jpg",
    "text": "Everyone, know it's a bit late in the year\nBut we have a new student joining US today'\nPlease introduce yourself:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p003.jpg",
    "text": "Hello?\nMy name is John:\nFm looking forward to meeting you alll"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p004.jpg",
    "text": "And [ hope we can get along'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p005.jpg",
    "text": "Ihad worked very hard to get into this school.\n3333 Ro6n\n11\nADOTOHH\n4"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p006.jpg",
    "text": "Many sleepless nights-\nCountless hours of studying _\nWith such difficult entrance exams, Iexpected academics to be the main focus at Wellston:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p007.jpg",
    "text": "Dnc 6\n5"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p008.jpg",
    "text": "Iexpected it to be different\nChatter"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p009.jpg",
    "text": "So math class is next?\nHi; John?\nFm Elaine: Welcome to Wellston:\nNCue C\nSMP"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p010.jpg",
    "text": "How's your first day so far?\nNot bad, Iguess:.\nWonderfull"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p011.jpg",
    "text": "So which school did you transfer from?\nErm, actually was home- schooled before this'\n0\nWoah really?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p012.jpg",
    "text": "We've never had one of those before:..\nHah:.. was feeling a bit lonely, so [ decided to try something new'\nWell; you've come to the"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p013.jpg",
    "text": "right place'\nAh That's great to know?\nBut I was wrong:-"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p014.jpg",
    "text": "So, John_\nThis place was just like the rest of the world."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p015.jpg",
    "text": "What kind of ability do you have?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p016.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p017.jpg",
    "text": "S;c lences"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p018.jpg",
    "text": "Well:.\nTo be completely honest._\nIdon't have one:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p019.jpg",
    "text": "What did you just say?\nErm:.~"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p020.jpg",
    "text": "Idon't have an abili-?\nICAN'T BELIEVE THIS?\nElaine?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p021.jpg",
    "text": "Are you alright?\nSN>"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p022.jpg",
    "text": "DON'T TOUCH ME?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p023.jpg",
    "text": "What a joke'\nThunp/"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p024.jpg",
    "text": "In this world, strength defines a person."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p025.jpg",
    "text": "Gross;\ncan't believe just spent all that time talking to someone like you:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p026.jpg",
    "text": "How boring: Another weakling:\nStupid new kid\nGetting our hopes up for nothing:\n3"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p027.jpg",
    "text": "And those without strength are crushed."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p028.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p029.jpg",
    "text": "Hey guys, Imnot looking for fight?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p030.jpg",
    "text": "Don't worry. Neither are we:\nWe're just here to educate you:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p031.jpg",
    "text": "So in this school, there's hierarchy that everyone follows\nAnd since you're a cripple, you're at the very bottom.\nYou must do evervthino"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p032.jpg",
    "text": "we say_\nThat girl? She's in my class!\n2 T4 Yeah: Otherwise; we'Il beat vour &-"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p033.jpg",
    "text": "HEY? CAN YOU HELP ME OUT HERE?'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p034.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p035.jpg",
    "text": "Those without strength are nothing:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p036.jpg",
    "text": "HEY NEW KID'\nPAY\nATTENTION WHEN WE SPEAK TO YOU?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p037.jpg",
    "text": "2"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p038.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p039.jpg",
    "text": "Xlh"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p040.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p041.jpg",
    "text": "PM"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p042.jpg",
    "text": "Hello?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_8\\unordinary_ep8_p043.jpg",
    "text": "unORDINARY - Episode 7 [end]\n@uru:chan\n@uruchanOFR Gutttec\nMolagrar"
